00:29.800 --> 00:32.080
<font color="white">MATURE JENNY:</font>
<font color="yellow">'With the return of Chummy,</font>

00:32.080 --> 00:34.880
<font color="yellow">'and her impending new arrival,</font>

00:34.880 --> 00:40.840
<font color="yellow">'life at Nonnatus House felt full</font>
<font color="yellow">of excitement and fresh promise.</font>

00:40.840 --> 00:44.720
<font color="yellow">'If clouds were gathering</font>
<font color="yellow">we could not see them.</font>

00:44.720 --> 00:46.960
<font color="yellow">'And if the winds of change</font>
<font color="yellow">were blowing...</font>

00:46.960 --> 00:50.320
<font color="yellow">'we had yet to feel the breeze.</font>

00:51.560 --> 00:53.200
<font color="yellow">'To us, the skies were blue.</font>

00:53.200 --> 00:55.440
<font color="yellow">'It was a warm and fruitful autumn</font>

00:55.440 --> 00:59.240
<font color="yellow">'and we took pleasure in assuming</font>

00:59.240 --> 01:02.160
<font color="yellow">'all was safely gathered in.'</font>

01:02.160 --> 01:04.000
<font color="white">I have to say,</font>

01:04.000 --> 01:07.120
<font color="white">it's frightfully kind of your ma</font>
<font color="white">to send all these baby clothes.</font>

01:07.120 --> 01:08.760
<font color="yellow">Were these really all yours,</font>
<font color="yellow">Cynthia?</font>

01:08.760 --> 01:11.280
<font color="cyan">I think my little brother</font>
<font color="cyan">wore some of them,</font>

01:11.280 --> 01:13.400
<font color="cyan">but they've been gathering dust</font>
<font color="cyan">for years.</font>

01:13.400 --> 01:15.720
<font color="cyan">Mother was telling me</font>
<font color="cyan">that the mother of pearl</font>

01:15.720 --> 01:19.360
<font color="cyan">buttons on the cardigans</font>
<font color="cyan">originally came from her...</font>

01:19.360 --> 01:21.880
<font color="white">CRUNCHING</font>

01:21.880 --> 01:23.720
<font color="cyan">..wedding dress.</font>

01:23.720 --> 01:25.640
<font color="white">Oh, no!</font>

01:25.640 --> 01:28.480
<font color="white">Oh, hang me, draw me,</font>
<font color="white">quarter me, Cynthia!</font>

01:28.480 --> 01:30.040
<font color="white">It was a family heirloom,</font>

01:30.040 --> 01:31.880
<font color="white">you should never have trusted me</font>
<font color="white">with it.</font>

01:31.880 --> 01:35.160
<font color="white">I'd have sooner wrapped</font>
<font color="white">Baby in brown paper.</font>

01:42.680 --> 01:44.360
<font color="lime">The morning post's arrived.</font>

01:46.760 --> 01:48.120
<font color="cyan">There's one for me!</font>

01:49.440 --> 01:52.480
<font color="cyan">It's from Sister Bernadette,</font>
<font color="cyan">in the Sana...</font>

01:52.480 --> 01:53.600
<font color="lime">Sanatorium.</font>

01:57.320 --> 02:00.680
<font color="cyan">It's a picture!</font>
<font color="cyan">Called The View From My Window.</font>

02:00.680 --> 02:03.760
<font color="cyan">She says, "Thank you very much</font>
<font color="cyan">for the dead butterfly,</font>

02:03.760 --> 02:06.680
<font color="cyan">"I have passed it onto the doctors</font>
<font color="cyan">here and I am awaiting</font>

02:06.680 --> 02:07.880
<font color="cyan">"their verdict.</font>

02:07.880 --> 02:10.639
<font color="cyan">"Thank your father</font>
<font color="cyan">for his kind letters,</font>

02:10.639 --> 02:13.400
<font color="cyan">"I shall reply to them</font>
<font color="cyan">in due course."</font>

02:13.400 --> 02:16.640
<font color="cyan">What does "in due course" mean?</font>

02:16.640 --> 02:20.240
<font color="lime">Sometimes, it means one day</font>
<font color="lime">and, sometimes, it means soon.</font>

02:21.680 --> 02:24.000
<font color="lime">Off you go now.</font>
<font color="lime">You'll be late for school.</font>

02:28.240 --> 02:31.040
<font color="white">Remember, Sister Monica Joan</font>
<font color="white">is not to be permitted to answer</font>

02:31.040 --> 02:32.080
<font color="white">the telephone.</font>

02:32.080 --> 02:34.960
<font color="white">So, whoever is on call</font>
<font color="white">must sit within earshot</font>

02:34.960 --> 02:36.360
<font color="white">and sight of the desk.</font>

02:36.360 --> 02:37.720
<font color="yellow">We do try.</font>

02:37.720 --> 02:40.200
<font color="yellow">It's getting harder and harder</font>
<font color="yellow">to keep her occupied...</font>

02:40.200 --> 02:42.880
<font color="cyan">Chummy needs things</font>
<font color="cyan">for the new arrival.</font>

02:42.880 --> 02:44.960
<font color="cyan">If we organised wool and needles,</font>

02:44.960 --> 02:47.280
<font color="cyan">Sister Monica Joan</font>
<font color="cyan">could be knitting baby clothes.</font>

02:47.280 --> 02:49.560
<font color="yellow">The only child they'd fit</font>
<font color="yellow">would be the mutant infant</font>

02:49.560 --> 02:51.600
<font color="yellow">from the Planet Of The Martians!</font>

02:51.600 --> 02:53.560
<font color="lime">Put her on blanket squares.</font>

02:53.560 --> 02:56.240
<font color="yellow">Blanket squares?</font>
<font color="yellow">She'd be bored to tears!</font>

02:56.240 --> 02:58.560
<font color="lime">She could knit them in her sleep,</font>
<font color="lime">just like any fool.</font>

02:58.560 --> 03:00.360
<font color="lime">Then she can sew them altogether,</font>

03:00.360 --> 03:03.440
<font color="lime">and some deserving person</font>
<font color="lime">will get a lovely bedspread.</font>

03:16.160 --> 03:17.720
<font color="white">Dolly?!</font>

03:17.720 --> 03:20.480
<font color="white">What's taken you so long?</font>
<font color="white">I've been on pins all day.</font>

03:20.480 --> 03:23.520
<font color="cyan">It's a five-hour drive from Gosport,</font>
<font color="cyan">Dad. Pat on the back would be nice.</font>

03:23.520 --> 03:26.560
<font color="white">Well, you haven't driven all the way</font>
<font color="white">yourself? Where's your husband?</font>

03:26.560 --> 03:29.760
<font color="cyan">He got a ship! Straight off,</font>
<font color="cyan">day after his discharge.</font>

03:29.760 --> 03:32.440
<font color="cyan">Merchant Navy ain't like the Royal,</font>
<font color="cyan">you get a charge,</font>

03:32.440 --> 03:33.640
<font color="cyan">you have to jump to.</font>

03:33.640 --> 03:36.440
<font color="white">But, Dolly, you know perfectly well</font>
<font color="white">you're in a...</font>

03:36.440 --> 03:38.000
<font color="white">interesting condition.</font>

03:38.000 --> 03:39.400
<font color="cyan">It's not that interesting.</font>

03:39.400 --> 03:41.480
<font color="cyan">Little scamp kept kicking me</font>
<font color="cyan">in the bladder,</font>

03:41.480 --> 03:43.440
<font color="cyan">made me drive all the faster!</font>

03:43.440 --> 03:46.320
<font color="cyan">Oh, I'm embarrassing</font>
<font color="cyan">you now, aren't I?</font>

03:46.320 --> 03:49.120
<font color="cyan">Come on, give us a kiss,</font>
<font color="cyan">you daft old bugger.</font>

03:49.120 --> 03:51.160
<font color="white">So, where d'you get this from?</font>

03:51.160 --> 03:53.680
<font color="cyan">I hired it, out our savings.</font>
<font color="cyan">Come on!</font>

03:56.800 --> 04:01.240
<font color="cyan">Ahh! Look, one grandson.</font>
<font color="cyan">Here you go.</font>

04:01.240 --> 04:03.920
<font color="white">Hey, hey! Hello, little fella!</font>

04:03.920 --> 04:06.880
<font color="cyan">He's got a name, Dad. Anthony.</font>

04:06.880 --> 04:08.840
<font color="white">Yeah, I know what you called him.</font>

04:08.840 --> 04:11.000
<font color="white">Come on, let's get you inside.</font>

04:16.680 --> 04:18.880
<font color="white">Whoa-hoa!</font>
<font color="white">You're a big boy, ain't ya?</font>

04:28.080 --> 04:30.880
<font color="lime">You do realise we'll be coming</font>
<font color="lime">to inspect your marital quarters</font>

04:30.880 --> 04:31.960
<font color="lime">soon, Chummy,</font>

04:31.960 --> 04:36.320
<font color="lime">making sure they're suitable</font>
<font color="lime">for home delivery and so forth!</font>

04:36.320 --> 04:39.560
<font color="yellow">Meanwhile, you're going to need</font>
<font color="yellow">a few more baby nighties, Chummy.</font>

04:39.560 --> 04:41.360
<font color="yellow">Time to set to with the Singer!</font>

04:41.360 --> 04:44.200
<font color="white">Baby's wardrobe's going to have</font>
<font color="white">to get in the queue, I'm afraid.</font>

04:44.200 --> 04:47.000
<font color="white">I still have to finish the maternity</font>
<font color="white">edition of my nurses uniform.</font>

04:47.000 --> 04:49.360
<font color="cyan">Are you sure</font>
<font color="cyan">you feel up to working, Chummy?</font>

04:49.360 --> 04:50.840
<font color="cyan">You've only a few weeks to go...</font>

04:50.840 --> 04:54.640
<font color="white">Oh, but I'm absolutely brimming with</font>
<font color="white">beans. We're terribly shorthanded!</font>

04:54.640 --> 04:57.320
<font color="white">I can't spend another day</font>
<font color="white">sitting round on my posterior,</font>

04:57.320 --> 05:00.000
<font color="white">watching the rest of you</font>
<font color="white">tie yourself in knots.</font>

05:01.400 --> 05:03.000
<font color="white">Gosh.</font>

05:03.000 --> 05:06.160
<font color="white">It rather reminds me of the night</font>
<font color="white">before a tiger shoot in Rajputan.</font>

05:06.160 --> 05:08.920
<font color="white">I could never sleep a wink,</font>
<font color="white">once all the nets and guns</font>

05:08.920 --> 05:10.760
<font color="white">had been laid out on the verandah.</font>

05:10.760 --> 05:14.720
<font color="lime">Chummy, you're having a baby,</font>
<font color="lime">not taking up blood sports!</font>

05:14.720 --> 05:16.400
<font color="cyan">Excuse me.</font>

05:18.680 --> 05:20.280
<font color="cyan">Sorry.</font>

05:20.280 --> 05:21.960
<font color="cyan">Only, er,</font>
<font color="cyan">somebody's in the bathroom,</font>

05:21.960 --> 05:23.760
<font color="cyan">and they've been there for ages.</font>

05:23.760 --> 05:24.960
<font color="cyan">I think it might be a nun.</font>

05:26.920 --> 05:28.040
<font color="white">Sorry.</font>

05:32.520 --> 05:35.400
<font color="white">THEY GIGGLE</font>

05:36.720 --> 05:39.600
<font color="white">I say, is there anybody in there?</font>

05:42.160 --> 05:43.720
<font color="lime">Yes, me!</font>

05:43.720 --> 05:45.720
<font color="lime">Can a woman</font>
<font color="lime">not have a bath in peace?</font>

05:45.720 --> 05:46.880
<font color="cyan">Sorry, Sister.</font>

05:46.880 --> 05:49.360
<font color="lime">What a good thing that</font>
<font color="lime">the Great Silence does not, in fact,</font>

05:49.360 --> 05:51.760
<font color="lime">commence for another 33 seconds,</font>

05:51.760 --> 05:54.960
<font color="lime">because it just gives me time</font>
<font color="lime">to warn you that my Sisters</font>

05:54.960 --> 05:57.440
<font color="lime">and I will not want</font>
<font color="lime">to come in here ever again</font>

05:57.440 --> 06:01.160
<font color="lime">and find the seat of a certain item</font>
<font color="lime">standing upright!</font>

06:01.160 --> 06:03.680
<font color="white">Oh, Sister Evangelina,</font>
<font color="white">I absolutely prom-...</font>

06:11.560 --> 06:13.880
<font color="white">It's not for long.</font>
<font color="cyan">It's for long enough.</font>

06:23.000 --> 06:25.480
<font color="white">Oh, this wretched girdle!</font>

06:25.480 --> 06:27.880
<font color="white">I've a bally good mind</font>
<font color="white">to write to Playtex.</font>

06:31.800 --> 06:32.840
<font color="yellow">Steady.</font>

06:35.160 --> 06:36.600
<font color="white">There.</font>

06:36.600 --> 06:39.080
<font color="white">Trixie, show me how to start it.</font>

06:40.600 --> 06:42.160
<font color="white">I know you know.</font>

06:48.080 --> 06:51.240
<font color="cyan">Engine trouble. Fetch a whip</font>
<font color="cyan">and thrash it like a horse!</font>

06:52.480 --> 06:54.360
<font color="yellow">Jimmy!</font>

06:54.360 --> 06:55.400
<font color="cyan">Hello, Jen!</font>

06:57.240 --> 06:59.240
<font color="cyan">Back from the tropics, Chummy?</font>
<font color="white">Rather.</font>

06:59.240 --> 07:02.720
<font color="white">And no jokes about excess baggage.</font>
<font color="white">I'm afraid we've heard them</font>

07:02.720 --> 07:05.320
<font color="white">all before.</font>
<font color="yellow">You must both be rather thirsty,</font>

07:05.320 --> 07:07.960
<font color="yellow">after brandishing that theodolite</font>
<font color="yellow">around all morning.</font>

07:07.960 --> 07:09.000
<font color="white">I should say so!</font>

07:09.000 --> 07:11.160
<font color="yellow">Can we persuade you</font>
<font color="yellow">to accept refreshments?</font>

07:11.160 --> 07:14.280
<font color="cyan">You'll have to bring them out here.</font>
<font color="cyan">We're under contract to the Council,</font>

07:14.280 --> 07:16.520
<font color="cyan">and I strongly suspect</font>
<font color="cyan">they have us followed.</font>

07:16.520 --> 07:20.120
<font color="white">No sneaking indoors,</font>
<font color="white">in the wake of pretty nurses, sadly.</font>

07:20.120 --> 07:21.160
<font color="cyan">Sorry, ladies.</font>

07:21.160 --> 07:24.480
<font color="cyan">This is Alec Jesmonde,</font>
<font color="cyan">my colleague and partner in crime.</font>

07:24.480 --> 07:28.120
<font color="cyan">This is Trixie and Chummy,</font>
<font color="cyan">both stalwarts of the nursing scene.</font>

07:28.120 --> 07:30.640
<font color="cyan">And this is Jenny,</font>
<font color="cyan">whom I've known forever.</font>

07:30.640 --> 07:31.760
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

07:31.760 --> 07:33.200
<font color="white">Hello.</font>

07:33.200 --> 07:35.760
<font color="yellow">So, will it be tea, or Nescafe?</font>

07:35.760 --> 07:37.680
<font color="white">Tea for me, if it's no trouble.</font>

07:37.680 --> 07:40.920
<font color="white">And he'll have Nescafe,</font>
<font color="white">strong enough to stand a spoon in.</font>

07:44.200 --> 07:46.400
<font color="cyan">Almond sponge!</font>

07:46.400 --> 07:48.600
<font color="white">Mrs B made you a cherry slab,</font>
<font color="white">as well,</font>

07:48.600 --> 07:51.240
<font color="white">but Sister Monica Joan</font>
<font color="white">chose to spare it the journey.</font>

07:54.680 --> 07:57.760
<font color="cyan">Sister. I had a set</font>
<font color="cyan">of X-rays taken yesterday.</font>

07:57.760 --> 08:00.240
<font color="cyan">And I've responded so well</font>
<font color="cyan">to the triple treatment</font>

08:00.240 --> 08:03.040
<font color="cyan">I no longer have active disease.</font>

08:03.040 --> 08:06.800
<font color="cyan">I'm going to be discharged</font>
<font color="cyan">next week, to convalesce at home.</font>

08:06.800 --> 08:10.240
<font color="white">Oh, that is the most wonderful news!</font>

08:11.360 --> 08:12.840
<font color="cyan">The difficulty is...</font>

08:14.120 --> 08:18.040
<font color="cyan">..that I'm still not</font>
<font color="cyan">entirely certain where my home is...</font>

08:18.040 --> 08:19.880
<font color="cyan">or ought to be.</font>

08:19.880 --> 08:21.520
<font color="white">Well, until you are certain,</font>

08:21.520 --> 08:25.160
<font color="white">your home is with us,</font>
<font color="white">amongst your sisters.</font>

08:25.160 --> 08:27.280
<font color="cyan">Could I trouble you</font>
<font color="cyan">for some clothes?</font>

08:27.280 --> 08:29.040
<font color="white">Clothes? Have you none here?</font>

08:30.440 --> 08:31.760
<font color="cyan">Only the habit.</font>

08:33.799 --> 08:35.880
<font color="cyan">And I don't feel able</font>
<font color="cyan">to wear that now.</font>

08:39.320 --> 08:41.559
<font color="yellow">I don't remember</font>
<font color="yellow">you liking strong coffee.</font>

08:41.559 --> 08:44.360
<font color="cyan">Exhaustion of the new parent.</font>
<font color="yellow">Boy or girl?</font>

08:44.360 --> 08:47.400
<font color="cyan">Little girl. Caroline Francesca.</font>

08:49.040 --> 08:51.640
<font color="cyan">Do you know, Jenny? That</font>
<font color="cyan">little baby's the sweetest thing</font>

08:51.640 --> 08:52.640
<font color="cyan">I ever saw.</font>

08:54.480 --> 08:57.840
<font color="cyan">She's got these lips that look</font>
<font color="cyan">as if she's about to kiss you.</font>

08:57.840 --> 09:00.120
<font color="cyan">And sometimes,</font>
<font color="cyan">when I bend over her cot,</font>

09:00.120 --> 09:04.720
<font color="cyan">her hands sort of startle</font>
<font color="cyan">and spread out like little starfish.</font>

09:07.280 --> 09:09.200
<font color="yellow">So it's turned out all right, then?</font>

09:11.160 --> 09:12.920
<font color="cyan">More all right than I dared hope.</font>

09:16.400 --> 09:18.960
<font color="yellow">You've made a full recovery</font>
<font color="yellow">from your illness?</font>

09:18.960 --> 09:21.760
<font color="yellow">I don't have to ask you that.</font>
<font color="yellow">I can see with my trained eye.</font>

09:21.760 --> 09:24.320
<font color="cyan">I've good reason</font>
<font color="cyan">to be grateful to your trained eye.</font>

09:24.320 --> 09:25.920
<font color="yellow">I didn't do anything.</font>

09:25.920 --> 09:27.320
<font color="cyan">You didn't leave my side.</font>

09:31.400 --> 09:33.680
<font color="yellow">I've grown to love nursing</font>
<font color="yellow">more and more.</font>

09:35.520 --> 09:39.360
<font color="yellow">I find myself feeling</font>
<font color="yellow">quite passionate about it -</font>

09:39.360 --> 09:42.440
<font color="yellow">what I can learn,</font>
<font color="yellow">what I can achieve.</font>

09:44.800 --> 09:48.160
<font color="yellow">It's become the thing</font>
<font color="yellow">that matters most to me.</font>

09:48.160 --> 09:50.040
<font color="cyan">Really?</font>

09:50.040 --> 09:51.040
<font color="yellow">Yes, really.</font>

09:52.440 --> 09:55.320
<font color="cyan">I would have thought there might</font>
<font color="cyan">be some lucky chap on the scene,</font>

09:55.320 --> 09:57.800
<font color="cyan">making your heart beat faster,</font>
<font color="cyan">all of that.</font>

09:57.800 --> 09:58.840
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

09:58.840 --> 10:01.760
<font color="cyan">Pity. </font><font color="yellow">I don't think so.</font>

10:04.720 --> 10:07.480
<font color="cyan">There's some badly-spalled brick</font>
<font color="cyan">on the front elevation.</font>

10:07.480 --> 10:09.680
<font color="cyan">You might need</font>
<font color="cyan">to come in close on that.</font>

10:11.520 --> 10:13.480
<font color="yellow">Why ARE you taking photographs?</font>

10:14.720 --> 10:17.880
<font color="cyan">Just making an inventory</font>
<font color="cyan">of the buildings in the district.</font>

10:17.880 --> 10:22.920
<font color="cyan">Great Gothic hulks,</font>
<font color="cyan">like these, are on their way</font>
<font color="cyan">to being historic curiosities.</font>

10:22.920 --> 10:25.080
<font color="yellow">When I first arrived,</font>
<font color="yellow">I was terrified.</font>

10:25.080 --> 10:28.560
<font color="yellow">Kept thinking a cloud of bats</font>
<font color="yellow">was going to fly out of the window.</font>

10:30.000 --> 10:31.480
<font color="yellow">Feels like home, now.</font>

10:33.640 --> 10:35.040
<font color="white">Smile for the birdie!</font>

10:45.240 --> 10:47.960
<font color="cyan">Oh, Dad,</font>
<font color="cyan">what d'you have to wear a suit for?</font>

10:47.960 --> 10:49.200
<font color="cyan">You smell of mothballs.</font>

10:49.200 --> 10:52.080
<font color="lime">I'm not bringing you just anywhere.</font>

10:52.080 --> 10:53.400
<font color="lime">Nurse Noakes!</font>

10:53.400 --> 10:56.840
<font color="white">What-ho, Fred.</font>
<font color="white">Oh, and this must be Dolly!</font>

10:56.840 --> 10:59.800
<font color="white">We've heard such a lot about you.</font>
<font color="white">You can come straight through.</font>

10:59.800 --> 11:02.760
<font color="cyan">Don't give me special treatment,</font>
<font color="cyan">just on account of His Nibs.</font>

11:02.760 --> 11:04.840
<font color="white">Not at all.</font>
<font color="white">You timed it like a dream.</font>

11:08.120 --> 11:09.160
<font color="cyan">'Ere.</font>

11:09.160 --> 11:10.760
<font color="lime">Oh!</font>

11:10.760 --> 11:12.040
<font color="cyan">Oh, here ya go.</font>

11:20.520 --> 11:24.080
<font color="white">So it's been decided that</font>
<font color="white">Sister Bernadette will not be</font>

11:24.080 --> 11:26.960
<font color="white">returning to us for the meanwhile,</font>
<font color="white">but will go to Chichester</font>

11:26.960 --> 11:32.600
<font color="white">as a house guest, while she considers</font>
<font color="white">her future with the Order. </font><font color="cyan">But why</font>
<font color="cyan">would she want to leave, at all?</font>

11:32.600 --> 11:37.520
<font color="cyan">Why would she give up now, when it's</font>
<font color="cyan">been her life for so many years?</font>

11:37.520 --> 11:40.680
<font color="white">"I have desired to go</font>
<font color="white">where springs not fail</font>

11:40.680 --> 11:44.040
<font color="white">"to fields where fly no sharp</font>
<font color="white">and sided hail,</font>

11:44.040 --> 11:45.760
<font color="white">"And a few lilies blow..."</font>

11:45.760 --> 11:47.960
<font color="lime">Keep your head down,</font>
<font color="lime">and get on with your knitting.</font>

11:47.960 --> 11:49.840
<font color="lime">Six squares do not a blanket make.</font>

11:49.840 --> 11:53.920
<font color="white">Gerard Manley Hopkins</font>
<font color="white">was not a professed religious,</font>

11:53.920 --> 11:59.880
<font color="white">yet he perceived the motives</font>
<font color="white">of many who choose holy orders.</font>

11:59.880 --> 12:04.920
<font color="white">And yet springs do fail,</font>
<font color="white">and hail does fall,</font>

12:04.920 --> 12:07.840
<font color="white">sharp enough to make us bleed.</font>

12:07.840 --> 12:10.800
<font color="cyan">Sister Bernadette is not</font>
<font color="cyan">suffering a loss of faith.</font>

12:10.800 --> 12:13.840
<font color="cyan">But she has come to question</font>
<font color="cyan">what God requires of her.</font>

12:13.840 --> 12:16.360
<font color="cyan">Beyond that,</font>
<font color="cyan">I'm not prepared to comment.</font>

12:20.480 --> 12:23.440
<font color="lime">I don't know why you don't let me</font>
<font color="lime">make a stand for that bath.</font>

12:23.440 --> 12:25.640
<font color="lime">You'll do your back in,</font>
<font color="lime">all that kneeling down.</font>

12:25.640 --> 12:28.440
<font color="cyan">Dad, he'd have it tipped over</font>
<font color="cyan">in no time!</font>

12:28.440 --> 12:31.800
<font color="lime">Oh, I made one for your mum,</font>
<font color="lime">and she was glad of it, I tell ya.</font>

12:31.800 --> 12:34.120
<font color="cyan">I often think of her at bath time.</font>

12:34.120 --> 12:36.880
<font color="lime">Ye. Happy memories.</font>

12:36.880 --> 12:39.120
<font color="cyan">They're the best ones,</font>
<font color="cyan">I'm telling you.</font>

12:40.800 --> 12:43.240
<font color="cyan">I drove past</font>
<font color="cyan">the bombsite on me way over</font>

12:43.240 --> 12:46.960
<font color="cyan">and it brought back</font>
<font color="cyan">the Blitz, like it was yesterday.</font>

12:46.960 --> 12:50.240
<font color="cyan">Me and Marlene being lifted out</font>
<font color="cyan">the rubble by a policeman,</font>

12:50.240 --> 12:52.200
<font color="cyan">still in our nighties.</font>

12:52.200 --> 12:53.920
<font color="lime">I should've been there, Doll.</font>

12:53.920 --> 12:55.520
<font color="cyan">You were fighting a war, Dad,</font>

12:55.520 --> 12:58.000
<font color="cyan">trying to stop that</font>
<font color="cyan">sort of thing from happening.</font>

12:58.000 --> 13:00.400
<font color="cyan">And it did stop happening,</font>
<font color="cyan">in the end.</font>

13:08.760 --> 13:10.840
<font color="lime">Sister Bernadette's suitcase.</font>

13:12.520 --> 13:14.960
<font color="lime">Found it in the store room.</font>

13:14.960 --> 13:18.360
<font color="lime">Logged in the book,</font>
<font color="lime">1st of July, 1948.</font>

13:19.640 --> 13:22.760
<font color="white">All her paperwork is here on file.</font>

13:22.760 --> 13:25.320
<font color="white">She came straight</font>
<font color="white">from the Nurse's Home at the London</font>

13:25.320 --> 13:27.400
<font color="white">and was here from her first day</font>
<font color="white">as a postulant.</font>

13:27.400 --> 13:30.760
<font color="white">The National Health was about</font>
<font color="white">to start, and she was needed.</font>

13:37.960 --> 13:39.800
<font color="lime">Utility shoes.</font>

13:39.800 --> 13:44.600
<font color="lime">She can't go walking out</font>
<font color="lime">into the world in these!</font>

13:44.600 --> 13:49.120
<font color="lime">Or any of this. She'll look dated.</font>

13:49.120 --> 13:51.720
<font color="lime">Dated, and out of place!</font>
<font color="lime">People will stare.</font>

13:51.720 --> 13:54.960
<font color="white">These are the only things</font>
<font color="white">in the world that belong to her.</font>

13:54.960 --> 13:56.520
<font color="white">And she has asked for them.</font>

13:59.120 --> 14:01.400
<font color="lime">I remember when she took First Vows,</font>

14:01.400 --> 14:03.560
<font color="lime">chose her religious name,</font>

14:03.560 --> 14:06.680
<font color="lime">I thought she'd had</font>
<font color="lime">her head turned by that film.</font>

14:06.680 --> 14:10.080
<font color="lime">We had a lot of that in the '40s.</font>
<font color="lime">Young girls would come here</font>

14:10.080 --> 14:11.920
<font color="lime">and you'd wonder what brought them.</font>

14:11.920 --> 14:15.240
<font color="lime">Was it The Lord,</font>
<font color="lime">the War or The Song Of Bernadette?</font>

14:16.360 --> 14:17.840
<font color="white">At least they came.</font>

14:19.000 --> 14:21.320
<font color="white">New vocations are dwindling,</font>
<font color="white">by the year.</font>

14:24.080 --> 14:27.400
<font color="lime">Well, no good grousing,</font>
<font color="lime">we must trust to Him.</font>

14:27.400 --> 14:30.680
<font color="lime">I'll give these shoes</font>
<font color="lime">a once over. Smell damp to me.</font>

14:40.400 --> 14:41.440
<font color="white">I say!</font>

14:43.880 --> 14:47.720
<font color="white">I've come to ask about that scooter.</font>
<font color="white">Is it still broken down?</font>

14:47.720 --> 14:49.160
<font color="yellow">I believe so, yes.</font>

14:49.160 --> 14:51.080
<font color="white">Well, I brought my toolkit along.</font>

14:51.080 --> 14:53.600
<font color="white">I haven't had my hands on a scooter</font>
<font color="white">since I was living in Rome,</font>

14:53.600 --> 14:56.560
<font color="white">and I'd love to play my part</font>
<font color="white">in restoring it to glory.</font>

14:56.560 --> 14:57.920
<font color="yellow">It's the property of the Order.</font>

14:57.920 --> 15:00.200
<font color="yellow">You'll have to talk</font>
<font color="yellow">to Sister Julienne.</font>

15:04.520 --> 15:07.720
<font color="white">THEY YELL</font>

15:09.000 --> 15:11.240
<font color="white">Pack! Pack! Pack!</font>

15:15.440 --> 15:17.520
<font color="lime">Will you all put a sock in it?!</font>

15:19.120 --> 15:21.320
<font color="lime">Have a bit of respect</font>
<font color="lime">for your Akela.</font>

15:21.320 --> 15:25.240
<font color="white">Today, we're starting</font>
<font color="white">work on our Handicraft badge.</font>

15:25.240 --> 15:26.440
<font color="white">ALL: Ohhh...</font>

15:26.440 --> 15:30.720
<font color="white">Yes. We're going to be learning</font>
<font color="white">the Japanese art of paper folding.</font>

15:30.720 --> 15:32.280
<font color="white">ALL: Booo...</font>

15:32.280 --> 15:37.280
<font color="white">And Dr Turner has kindly agreed</font>
<font color="white">to come along and show us all</font>

15:37.280 --> 15:39.440
<font color="white">how to make an origami frog!</font>

15:41.760 --> 15:43.040
<font color="white">And here he is!</font>

15:43.040 --> 15:44.600
<font color="lime">Sorry I'm late.</font>

15:44.600 --> 15:47.720
<font color="white">Timothy, there's a box</font>
<font color="white">of paper squares on top of the piano,</font>

15:47.720 --> 15:49.400
<font color="white">make sure everyone gets one.</font>

15:49.400 --> 15:53.080
<font color="white">And I want you to concentrate</font>
<font color="white">very hard on Dr Turner's</font>

15:53.080 --> 15:57.000
<font color="white">instructions, because if you follow</font>
<font color="white">them correctly, there's a simply</font>

15:57.000 --> 16:00.720
<font color="white">marvellous bit at the end, where you</font>
<font color="white">get to blow into a frog's bottom...</font>

16:01.960 --> 16:03.800
<font color="white">..and make it three dimensional.</font>

16:14.200 --> 16:15.320
<font color="cyan">Sleepy boy.</font>

16:19.720 --> 16:22.840
<font color="lime">Now, you should have something</font>
<font color="lime">that looks a bit like a diamond.</font>

16:22.840 --> 16:27.640
<font color="lime">If you fold each of the four sides</font>
<font color="lime">inwards, making a long sharp crease</font>

16:27.640 --> 16:33.520
<font color="lime">with your thumbnail, you should</font>
<font color="lime">start to see the legs take shape.</font>

16:33.520 --> 16:37.840
<font color="white">I reckon mine's got three!</font>
<font color="white">LAUGHTER</font>

16:37.840 --> 16:38.880
<font color="cyan">Dad!</font>

16:38.880 --> 16:42.320
<font color="cyan">I'm not making you</font>
<font color="cyan">a packed tea again,</font>

16:42.320 --> 16:44.840
<font color="cyan">if you're going to keep leaving it</font>
<font color="cyan">on the draining board!</font>

16:44.840 --> 16:48.800
<font color="lime">Ah, I come straight from Nonnatus!</font>
<font color="cyan">Evening, Nurse.</font>

16:50.000 --> 16:53.160
<font color="cyan">Wouldn't mind, only there's</font>
<font color="cyan">a steak pie in there. Homemade.</font>

16:53.160 --> 16:56.760
<font color="cyan">I was all day stood in the kitchen,</font>
<font color="cyan">prising tubing out of kidneys.</font>

16:56.760 --> 17:00.000
<font color="cyan">My feet are that swollen,</font>
<font color="cyan">I had to come here in me slippers!</font>

17:01.480 --> 17:02.480
<font color="white">May I see?</font>

17:04.960 --> 17:07.319
<font color="cyan">Got some right funny looks,</font>
<font color="cyan">I can tell you.</font>

17:11.079 --> 17:14.440
<font color="white">I need you to take</font>
<font color="white">a quick tinkle...in this.</font>

17:16.240 --> 17:17.680
<font color="cyan">But that's a good teacup!</font>

17:17.680 --> 17:20.000
<font color="white">I need to carry out</font>
<font color="white">some routine tests.</font>

17:20.000 --> 17:22.160
<font color="white">If everything's shipshape,</font>

17:22.160 --> 17:25.119
<font color="white">you can just pop along to clinic</font>
<font color="white">as usual on Tuesday.</font>

17:25.119 --> 17:28.119
<font color="cyan">All right... I don't suppose</font>
<font color="cyan">you got any aspirin in there?</font>

17:28.119 --> 17:29.560
<font color="cyan">Me head's splitting.</font>

17:39.600 --> 17:44.360
<font color="white">Oh, hello! The, um, problem</font>
<font color="white">seems to be with the choke lever.</font>

17:44.360 --> 17:48.560
<font color="white">It's come adrift from the carburettor</font>
<font color="white">on the right side of the engine.</font>

17:48.560 --> 17:50.480
<font color="yellow">Gosh. No wonder it won't go.</font>

17:50.480 --> 17:52.200
<font color="white">Well, I've had</font>
<font color="white">to unscrew the air filter,</font>

17:52.200 --> 17:54.280
<font color="white">so I can access the connection point.</font>

17:56.040 --> 17:57.160
<font color="yellow">I'll tell Sister Julienne.</font>

17:57.160 --> 17:58.960
<font color="yellow">She said to say</font>
<font color="yellow">thank you for your help,</font>

17:58.960 --> 18:01.160
<font color="yellow">and to bring you</font>
<font color="yellow">some tea and biscuits.</font>

18:01.160 --> 18:02.760
<font color="white">Ah, biscuits? Marvellous.</font>

18:02.760 --> 18:04.360
<font color="yellow">Garibaldi, I'm afraid.</font>

18:04.360 --> 18:07.600
<font color="white">We used to call them fly cemeteries,</font>
<font color="white">when we were kids.</font>

18:07.600 --> 18:09.200
<font color="yellow">So did we!</font>

18:10.320 --> 18:12.280
<font color="yellow">We were always pleased</font>
<font color="yellow">to see them, though.</font>

18:12.280 --> 18:14.480
<font color="yellow">Any port in a storm,</font>
<font color="yellow">during rationing.</font>

18:17.000 --> 18:18.960
<font color="white">If I get this engine going,</font>

18:18.960 --> 18:21.920
<font color="white">I'll need to take it for a spin,</font>
<font color="white">to make sure it's properly tuned.</font>

18:21.920 --> 18:23.680
<font color="white">You can come with me if you like.</font>

18:25.200 --> 18:27.200
<font color="yellow">I'm afraid I'm on call.</font>

18:27.200 --> 18:29.320
<font color="yellow">Which would make it most improper.</font>

18:37.880 --> 18:39.720
<font color="lime">Stop kicking him, Jack.</font>

18:39.720 --> 18:43.200
<font color="lime">Come on lads, left to right.</font>
<font color="lime">Really sharp folds...</font>

18:43.200 --> 18:46.480
<font color="lime">Sit still. No skylarking. Gary!</font>

18:49.240 --> 18:53.160
<font color="white">I shall be back in two shakes</font>
<font color="white">of a lamb's tail.</font>

18:53.160 --> 18:56.480
<font color="lime">Now, if you've been following</font>
<font color="lime">the instructions correctly,</font>

18:56.480 --> 18:59.120
<font color="lime">you should have something</font>
<font color="lime">that looks like this.</font>

18:59.120 --> 19:01.280
<font color="white">It looks nothing like a frog!</font>

19:01.280 --> 19:03.600
<font color="white">It looks like a tortoise</font>
<font color="white">what's been run over!</font>

19:03.600 --> 19:07.000
<font color="lime">Ah, what you have to do now</font>
<font color="lime">is turn it around this way,</font>

19:07.000 --> 19:08.680
<font color="lime">blow into the hole...</font>

19:14.000 --> 19:15.640
<font color="lime">And lo and behold!</font>

19:15.640 --> 19:19.720
<font color="lime">A fully inflatable,</font>
<font color="lime">three-dimensional amphibian!</font>

19:19.720 --> 19:23.600
<font color="white">Doctor Turner. May I trouble you</font>
<font color="white">to come into the kitchen? </font><font color="lime">Of course.</font>

19:27.960 --> 19:31.800
<font color="cyan">I don't need all this fuss!</font>
<font color="cyan">I walked round here no bother!</font>

19:31.800 --> 19:33.280
<font color="white">Dolly.</font>

19:33.280 --> 19:35.840
<font color="white">As Doctor explained,</font>
<font color="white">toxaemia is a treatable condition,</font>

19:35.840 --> 19:38.440
<font color="white">but we do need to get you somewhere</font>
<font color="white">where you can rest in peace</font>

19:38.440 --> 19:41.480
<font color="white">and quiet, and where Doctor</font>
<font color="white">can carry out more tests.</font>

19:41.480 --> 19:42.720
<font color="cyan">What about Anthony?</font>

19:45.160 --> 19:47.840
<font color="white">Well, I'm quite sure</font>
<font color="white">you can leave him to Grandpa.</font>

19:47.840 --> 19:50.760
<font color="white">A baby will be a cakewalk compared</font>
<font color="white">to the boiler at Nonnatus House.</font>

19:50.760 --> 19:51.880
<font color="yellow">What about me?</font>

19:51.880 --> 19:54.400
<font color="lime">Go and help Bagheera</font>
<font color="lime">with the clearing up.</font>

19:58.200 --> 19:59.200
<font color="cyan">I'm in.</font>

20:09.920 --> 20:13.200
<font color="lime">Your Granddad's boy, yes you are.</font>

20:13.200 --> 20:17.360
<font color="lime">Yeah, that's it, lad.</font>
<font color="lime">Put some wellie into it.</font>

20:17.360 --> 20:21.040
<font color="white">I've had to learn to be good at all</font>
<font color="white">sorts of things since my mum died.</font>

20:21.040 --> 20:23.320
<font color="white">My dad says,</font>
<font color="white">"Learn to be independent.</font>

20:23.320 --> 20:25.200
<font color="white">"One day you might be on your own."</font>

20:27.040 --> 20:28.520
<font color="lime">Uh-oh...</font>

20:28.520 --> 20:30.120
<font color="lime">Uhhhhh!</font>

20:35.160 --> 20:37.560
<font color="cyan">I've been overdoing it, that's all.</font>

20:38.760 --> 20:42.040
<font color="white">I know</font>
<font color="white">it's a perfectly beastly shock.</font>

20:42.040 --> 20:43.680
<font color="white">And so unfair.</font>

20:43.680 --> 20:46.600
<font color="white">It's frightfully uncommon to have</font>
<font color="white">toxaemia with a second babe,</font>

20:46.600 --> 20:48.800
<font color="white">when all went smoothly</font>
<font color="white">with the first.</font>

20:48.800 --> 20:52.680
<font color="cyan">I'm worried my Dad won't know</font>
<font color="cyan">what to do with Anthony.</font>

20:52.680 --> 20:53.800
<font color="white">Come, come.</font>

20:56.840 --> 21:01.200
<font color="white">When I was at school, I had this</font>
<font color="white">perfectly terrifying old matron,</font>

21:01.200 --> 21:05.160
<font color="white">but she used to say,</font>
<font color="white">if ever one found oneself in a tight</font>

21:05.160 --> 21:09.400
<font color="white">squeeze, one could keep</font>
<font color="white">one's composure by reciting slowly</font>

21:09.400 --> 21:13.680
<font color="white">Psalm 123, taking deep breaths</font>
<font color="white">between each line.</font>

21:13.680 --> 21:16.680
<font color="cyan">I don't know Psalm 123.</font>

21:18.280 --> 21:21.760
<font color="white">Well, I'm quite sure your</font>
<font color="white">favourite song would do the trick.</font>

21:27.120 --> 21:30.080
<font color="cyan"># Catch a falling star</font>

21:30.080 --> 21:33.280
<font color="cyan"># And put it in your pocket</font>

21:33.280 --> 21:37.240
<font color="cyan"># Never let it fade away. #</font>

21:37.240 --> 21:39.680
<font color="white">Bravo! Deep breaths.</font>

21:41.080 --> 21:43.200
<font color="cyan"># Catch a falling star</font>

21:43.200 --> 21:46.640
<font color="cyan"># And put it in your pocket</font>

21:46.640 --> 21:50.080
<font color="cyan"># Save it for a rainy day. #</font>

21:50.080 --> 21:54.040
<font color="white">That sounds far more jolly</font>
<font color="white">than a dreary old psalm.</font>

21:54.040 --> 21:56.760
<font color="white">I shall have to listen out</font>
<font color="white">for it on the wireless.</font>

21:58.760 --> 22:00.160
<font color="lime">When did this come?</font>

22:00.160 --> 22:02.280
<font color="white">This morning.</font>
<font color="white">There's been no warning.</font>

22:02.280 --> 22:03.800
<font color="white">No indication of any kind.</font>

22:03.800 --> 22:06.800
<font color="lime">It's not enough we've had all the</font>
<font color="lime">shenanigans with Sister Bernadette,</font>

22:06.800 --> 22:08.760
<font color="lime">this just puts the tin hat on it!</font>

22:08.760 --> 22:09.760
<font color="white">Sister...</font>

22:11.680 --> 22:13.760
<font color="white">I suggest we keep this to ourselves</font>

22:13.760 --> 22:16.320
<font color="white">until the situation</font>
<font color="white">becomes a little clearer.</font>

22:24.080 --> 22:27.440
<font color="white">Wakey-wakey, campers.</font>
<font color="white">Rise and shine!</font>

22:27.440 --> 22:29.160
<font color="cyan">Already had breakfast in bed.</font>

22:29.160 --> 22:32.440
<font color="cyan">And I put you down</font>
<font color="cyan">for the knobbly knees contest.</font>

22:33.520 --> 22:35.200
<font color="cyan">Oh, 'ello!</font>

22:36.600 --> 22:38.640
<font color="cyan">What you washed him in? </font><font color="white">Silvikrin.</font>

22:38.640 --> 22:40.880
<font color="cyan">All over? Dad, it's shampoo!</font>

22:40.880 --> 22:43.840
<font color="lime">Fred, I'm sorry,</font>
<font color="lime">but you're interrupting bed rest.</font>

22:43.840 --> 22:46.240
<font color="white">Sorry, Doctor.</font>
<font color="cyan">But I won't get any rest wondering</font>

22:46.240 --> 22:48.680
<font color="cyan">what bloody buggerlugs</font>
<font color="cyan">is up to with my baby!</font>

22:48.680 --> 22:52.960
<font color="lime">Men aren't totally incompetent,</font>
<font color="lime">Mrs Smart. And babies do bounce.</font>

22:52.960 --> 22:55.280
<font color="cyan">Only when you drop 'em!</font>

22:55.280 --> 22:57.920
<font color="white">Doctor, I've just</font>
<font color="white">had a tiny thoughtette.</font>

22:57.920 --> 23:00.840
<font color="white">Dolly, if you could get</font>
<font color="white">a bally good look at Anthony</font>

23:00.840 --> 23:04.320
<font color="white">for two whole minutes every day,</font>
<font color="white">at precisely the same time -</font>

23:04.320 --> 23:08.360
<font color="white">say eleven o'clock in the morning -</font>
<font color="white">would that be enough to reassure you?</font>

23:08.360 --> 23:10.640
<font color="cyan">Well, that depends, don't it?</font>

23:10.640 --> 23:12.480
<font color="white">But if everything</font>
<font color="white">was in apple-pie order,</font>

23:12.480 --> 23:16.440
<font color="white">with Anthony spotlessly clean,</font>
<font color="white">well-fed and beaming?</font>

23:16.440 --> 23:19.360
<font color="white">Wouldn't that make you feel better?</font>
<font color="cyan">Yeah... I s'pose.</font>

23:19.360 --> 23:21.640
<font color="lime">Well, Nurse Noakes</font>
<font color="lime">clearly has a plan.</font>

23:21.640 --> 23:24.360
<font color="lime">And I'm sure</font>
<font color="lime">nobody's going to argue with her.</font>

23:28.040 --> 23:29.640
<font color="white"># Catch a falling star</font>

23:29.640 --> 23:32.040
<font color="white"># And put it in your pocket</font>

23:32.040 --> 23:35.960
