<font color="lime">Never let it fade away</font>

23:35.960 --> 23:39.480
<font color="white"># Catch a falling star</font>
<font color="white">And put it in your pocket</font>

23:39.480 --> 23:45.520
<font color="white"># Save it for a rainy day</font>
<font color="lime">Save it for a rainy day</font>

23:45.520 --> 23:50.000
<font color="white"># For love may come</font>
<font color="white">and tap you on the shoulder</font>

23:50.000 --> 23:52.720
<font color="white"># Some starless night</font>

23:52.720 --> 23:58.280
<font color="white"># And just in case you feel</font>
<font color="white">You want to hold her</font>

23:58.280 --> 24:02.200
<font color="white"># You'll have a pocketful</font>
<font color="white">of starlight</font>

24:02.200 --> 24:06.200
<font color="lime"># Pocketful of starlight</font>

24:06.200 --> 24:10.080
<font color="white"># Catch a falling star</font>
<font color="white">And put it in your pocket</font>

24:10.080 --> 24:13.520
<font color="white"># Never let it fade away</font>

24:13.520 --> 24:15.920
<font color="white"># Catch a falling star and... #</font>

24:15.920 --> 24:17.360
<font color="lime">Come on, then.</font>

24:17.360 --> 24:20.560
<font color="white"># ..pocket, save it for a rainy day</font>

24:20.560 --> 24:24.200
<font color="lime"># Save it for a rainy day</font>
<font color="lime">Save it for a rainy...</font>

24:24.200 --> 24:25.840
<font color="lime"># Rainy, rainy day</font>

24:25.840 --> 24:30.320
<font color="white"># For when your troubles</font>
<font color="white">start multiplying</font>

24:30.320 --> 24:32.960
<font color="white"># And they just might</font>

24:34.200 --> 24:38.320
<font color="white"># It's easy to forget them</font>
<font color="white">Without trying</font>

24:38.320 --> 24:41.200
<font color="white"># With just a pocketful</font>
<font color="white">of starlight. #</font>

24:41.200 --> 24:42.600
<font color="white">I won't give up!</font>

24:43.760 --> 24:46.240
<font color="yellow">On the carburettor</font>
<font color="yellow">or the choke lever?</font>

24:46.240 --> 24:47.760
<font color="white">On you!</font>

24:47.760 --> 24:49.840
<font color="white">My ultimate goal is to take you out,</font>

24:49.840 --> 24:52.360
<font color="white">but quite frankly,</font>
<font color="white">I'd settle for a smile.</font>

24:52.360 --> 24:55.320
<font color="yellow">You'll have to excuse me.</font>
<font color="yellow">I'm on my rounds.</font>

24:57.640 --> 25:01.160
<font color="white">MOTOR SPLUTTERS THEN CUTS OUT</font>

25:01.160 --> 25:07.280
<font color="white"># Save it for a rainy day. #</font>

25:12.440 --> 25:15.920
<font color="white">The day has dawned.</font>
<font color="white">Arrange a toll of bells.</font>

25:15.920 --> 25:19.480
<font color="lime">What's happening?</font>
<font color="white">I can't get my girdle on.</font>

25:19.480 --> 25:21.040
<font color="lime">D'you want me to pull on the straps?</font>

25:21.040 --> 25:23.480
<font color="white">Peter, Charles Atlas</font>
<font color="white">could pull on the straps,</font>

25:23.480 --> 25:25.440
<font color="white">they'd never meet across this tum!</font>

25:36.280 --> 25:38.720
<font color="lime">And that's the end of that.</font>

25:38.720 --> 25:39.760
<font color="white">Yes.</font>

25:41.040 --> 25:42.600
<font color="white">What's it the start of?</font>

25:54.480 --> 25:56.520
<font color="lime">I think it's perfectly absurd.</font>

25:56.520 --> 25:59.520
<font color="lime">Sister Monica Joan's supposed</font>
<font color="lime">to be knitting blanket squares,</font>

25:59.520 --> 26:00.640
<font color="lime">to keep her out of bother.</font>

26:00.640 --> 26:03.000
<font color="yellow">But she's slowing down.</font>

26:03.000 --> 26:05.280
<font color="yellow">So she'll never knit enough</font>
<font color="yellow">to make a whole blanket,</font>

26:05.280 --> 26:07.240
<font color="yellow">and realise it's all make believe.</font>

26:07.240 --> 26:10.760
<font color="lime">Can't imagine who would want</font>
<font color="lime">such a repellent thing, in any case.</font>

26:10.760 --> 26:15.320
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS</font>

26:15.320 --> 26:17.240
<font color="lime">Nonnatus House, midwife speaking.</font>

26:17.240 --> 26:18.960
<font color="cyan">Hello, Trixie.</font>

26:18.960 --> 26:21.080
<font color="lime">Oh, hello, Jimmy.</font>

26:21.080 --> 26:23.640
<font color="lime">I thought your hour of need</font>
<font color="lime">had passed.</font>

26:23.640 --> 26:26.040
<font color="cyan">Can I speak to Jenny, please?</font>

26:31.480 --> 26:32.480
<font color="yellow">Hello, Jimmy.</font>

26:32.480 --> 26:33.640
<font color="cyan">Jenny! Listen...</font>

26:33.640 --> 26:36.760
<font color="cyan">Some friends and I have put</font>
<font color="cyan">a bit of jazz group together</font>

26:36.760 --> 26:40.240
<font color="cyan">and we've persuaded</font>
<font color="cyan">Caesar Jack's club to let us</font>
<font color="cyan">do a set on Thursday night.</font>

26:41.320 --> 26:43.880
<font color="yellow">I didn't know</font>
<font color="yellow">you played any instruments.</font>

26:43.880 --> 26:46.000
<font color="cyan">I tried the double bass</font>
<font color="cyan">and settled on the drums.</font>

26:46.000 --> 26:48.840
<font color="cyan">The thing is, Jen, we're going</font>
<font color="cyan">to look like utter chumps,</font>

26:48.840 --> 26:53.720
<font color="cyan">if no-one turns up to hear us.</font>
<font color="cyan">And I hoped you might bring</font>
<font color="cyan">some of your friends along.</font>

26:53.720 --> 26:56.720
<font color="yellow">Well, I'm not sure</font>
<font color="yellow">how many I could muster.</font>

26:56.720 --> 26:58.480
<font color="cyan">Bring anyone. Bring the nuns.</font>

26:58.480 --> 27:00.080
<font color="cyan">Tell them I'll give them free beer.</font>

27:01.240 --> 27:04.120
<font color="lime">We'll have a Babycham, thank you</font>
<font color="lime">very much, and we expect to see them</font>

27:04.120 --> 27:07.600
<font color="lime">lined up at the bar, with</font>
<font color="lime">a whisky chaser for Sister Julienne.</font>

27:11.520 --> 27:13.000
<font color="cyan">Marvellous!</font>

27:18.360 --> 27:21.600
<font color="white">Well, Dolly, I was always</font>
<font color="white">an utter dunce at maths,</font>

27:21.600 --> 27:25.440
<font color="white">but even I can see these measurements</font>
<font color="white">are shaping up delightfully.</font>

27:26.440 --> 27:28.040
<font color="cyan">You given much thought to names yet?</font>

27:28.040 --> 27:30.880
<font color="white">Oh, gosh, no. Far too busy!</font>

27:30.880 --> 27:33.000
<font color="white">I take it Anthony</font>
<font color="white">was called after his papa?</font>

27:33.000 --> 27:35.320
<font color="cyan">Oh, no, after me father-in-law.</font>

27:35.320 --> 27:38.800
<font color="cyan">My dad went mad. Well, silent mad.</font>

27:38.800 --> 27:40.760
<font color="cyan">He never said nothing at the time,</font>

27:40.760 --> 27:43.280
<font color="cyan">but I don't reckon he's said it</font>
<font color="cyan">from that day to this.</font>

27:43.280 --> 27:44.920
<font color="cyan">He always calls him The Nipper.</font>

27:44.920 --> 27:47.000
<font color="white">Oh, but he absolutely dotes on him!</font>

27:47.000 --> 27:49.080
<font color="cyan">I don't doubt it.</font>

27:49.080 --> 27:51.680
<font color="cyan">It's a funny old fandangle, family.</font>

27:51.680 --> 27:55.120
<font color="cyan">Sometimes, I'm telling you,</font>
<font color="cyan">it's like trying to plait soot.</font>

27:56.200 --> 27:58.400
<font color="white">Yes. I suppose it is.</font>

28:00.200 --> 28:03.080
<font color="lime">For pity's sake, Jenny,</font>
<font color="lime">stop pulling your sweater down.</font>

28:03.080 --> 28:05.480
<font color="lime">People will think</font>
<font color="lime">you've had some sort of an accident!</font>

28:05.480 --> 28:07.640
<font color="yellow">Trixie, I never go out</font>
<font color="yellow">for the evening in slacks!</font>

28:07.640 --> 28:10.000
<font color="lime">I believe Princess Margaret</font>
<font color="lime">does it all the time.</font>

28:10.000 --> 28:12.400
<font color="yellow">See? Even Jane knows</font>
<font color="yellow">what's what in a jazz club.</font>

28:12.400 --> 28:13.800
<font color="lime">I read an article in Woman's Own.</font>

28:13.800 --> 28:16.240
<font color="lime">That's why I'm wearing</font>
<font color="lime">a polo neck sweater.</font>

28:20.600 --> 28:22.200
<font color="cyan">Jimmy!</font>

28:26.800 --> 28:29.520
<font color="white">SHE LAUGHS</font>

28:29.520 --> 28:31.640
<font color="cyan">Thank you!</font>

28:31.640 --> 28:35.640
<font color="yellow">Jenny! Jenny! Babycham.</font>

28:37.800 --> 28:39.600
<font color="yellow">Jane. Drink. </font><font color="lime">Oh. Thank you.</font>

28:42.560 --> 28:45.320
<font color="white">I had a letter from Mater today.</font>

28:45.320 --> 28:46.840
<font color="lime">That's nice.</font>

28:46.840 --> 28:48.760
<font color="white">She enclosed a cheque for ten pounds,</font>

28:48.760 --> 28:50.960
<font color="white">said she hoped things</font>
<font color="white">wouldn't be too frightful,</font>

28:50.960 --> 28:53.880
<font color="white">and closed by saying</font>
<font color="white">she was dashing off to bridge.</font>

28:53.880 --> 28:55.600
<font color="lime">Madeira's a long way off.</font>

28:55.600 --> 28:57.920
<font color="lime">For which, mercy may we give thanks.</font>

28:57.920 --> 29:00.720
<font color="white">She was never going</font>
<font color="white">to pitch up with a cold chicken</font>

29:00.720 --> 29:02.720
<font color="white">and rinse baby's napkins through.</font>

29:02.720 --> 29:06.040
<font color="white">But I feel so frightfully</font>
<font color="white">disconnected from any sort of...</font>

29:07.280 --> 29:08.200
<font color="white">..advice.</font>

29:08.200 --> 29:10.680
<font color="white">I was trying to think</font>
<font color="white">of nursery rhymes today -</font>

29:10.680 --> 29:12.840
<font color="white">songs my mother taught me,</font>
<font color="white">all of that.</font>

29:14.480 --> 29:16.920
<font color="white">The only lullabies</font>
<font color="white">I know are in Hindi!</font>

29:16.920 --> 29:18.840
<font color="lime">I shall look forward to that.</font>

29:20.720 --> 29:21.800
<font color="white">Peter...</font>

29:23.400 --> 29:25.400
<font color="white">What have we got to give this child?</font>

29:26.640 --> 29:30.320
<font color="white">We've no proper home. No money.</font>
<font color="white">Not much in the way of family,</font>

29:30.320 --> 29:32.760
<font color="white">now your parents have moved</font>
<font color="white">to Walton-on-the-Naze.</font>

29:32.760 --> 29:34.920
<font color="lime">You're going to be</font>
<font color="lime">a wonderful mother, Camilla.</font>

29:34.920 --> 29:37.320
<font color="lime">You're a nurse,</font>
<font color="lime">you've got half the skills off pat.</font>

29:37.320 --> 29:40.160
<font color="white">Oh, yes. Well, you just wait</font>
<font color="white">till I give myself castor oil</font>

29:40.160 --> 29:41.520
<font color="white">and advisory pamphlets!</font>

29:45.000 --> 29:47.000
<font color="lime">Have you got any pamphlets</font>
<font color="lime">on how to calm down?</font>

29:47.000 --> 29:49.560
<font color="lime">You're working all the hairs</font>
<font color="lime">from the brush into the gloss.</font>

29:49.560 --> 29:50.520
<font color="white">Sorry.</font>

29:55.520 --> 29:58.040
<font color="yellow">Another two Babychams</font>
<font color="yellow">and a bitter lemon, please.</font>

29:58.040 --> 29:59.880
<font color="cyan">Who's drinking bitter lemon?</font>

29:59.880 --> 30:01.800
<font color="yellow">Me.</font>

30:01.800 --> 30:04.360
<font color="yellow">Meanwhile, Cynthia</font>
<font color="yellow">isn't drinking anything</font>

30:04.360 --> 30:06.520
<font color="yellow">because she doesn't like</font>
<font color="yellow">the toilets.</font>

30:19.920 --> 30:22.440
<font color="cyan">I am sorry I didn't tell you</font>
<font color="cyan">Alec was in the band.</font>

30:24.680 --> 30:26.560
<font color="cyan">He really likes you.</font>

30:26.560 --> 30:29.000
<font color="yellow">I don't like being bullied</font>
<font color="yellow">into things.</font>

30:29.000 --> 30:32.680
<font color="cyan">Jenny, I'm on your side.</font>
<font color="cyan">Can't you see that?</font>

30:34.080 --> 30:36.400
<font color="cyan">You said it to me once -</font>
<font color="cyan">you're my friend,</font>

30:36.400 --> 30:37.960
<font color="cyan">and I want you to be happy.</font>

30:39.520 --> 30:43.760
<font color="cyan">And, one day - maybe this week,</font>
<font color="cyan">maybe next year -</font>

30:43.760 --> 30:46.520
<font color="cyan">you're going to be happy</font>
<font color="cyan">with someone else.</font>

30:46.520 --> 30:48.520
<font color="cyan">And I'm going to be glad.</font>

30:51.160 --> 30:52.160
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

30:52.160 --> 30:54.040
<font color="cyan">Jen, I'm determined to be glad!</font>

30:56.000 --> 30:58.040
<font color="cyan">Falling for someone</font>
<font color="cyan">would set you free!</font>

30:58.040 --> 31:00.880
<font color="cyan">From a life of drinking bitter lemon</font>
<font color="cyan">and your own daft rules,</font>

31:00.880 --> 31:02.800
<font color="cyan">if nothing else!</font>

31:02.800 --> 31:04.880
<font color="white">Three and four pence, please, miss.</font>

31:04.880 --> 31:06.560
<font color="yellow">He'll get these.</font>

31:06.560 --> 31:08.360
<font color="yellow">And have a double for yourself.</font>

31:08.360 --> 31:11.120
<font color="white">Thank you very much.</font>
<font color="cyan">A...another one. </font><font color="white">Of course.</font>

31:11.120 --> 31:14.160
<font color="yellow">I'm afraid we're going</font>
<font color="yellow">to have to dance together</font>

31:14.160 --> 31:16.080
<font color="yellow">or I'll never hear the end of it.</font>

31:16.080 --> 31:18.480
<font color="yellow">And neither,</font>
<font color="yellow">I strongly suspect, will you.</font>

31:18.480 --> 31:19.720
<font color="white">Do you want to dance?</font>

31:19.720 --> 31:21.920
<font color="yellow">No. Not really.</font>

31:21.920 --> 31:24.640
<font color="yellow">But dancing seems to be</font>
<font color="yellow">the thing that people do</font>

31:24.640 --> 31:29.520
<font color="yellow">when they don't want to be</font>
<font color="yellow">thought rude, or stand-offish, or...</font>

31:29.520 --> 31:33.000
<font color="yellow">whatever unfortunate impression</font>
<font color="yellow">I might have given so far.</font>

31:33.000 --> 31:36.200
<font color="yellow">Dancing is what people do when....</font>

31:36.200 --> 31:38.880
<font color="white">They think</font>
<font color="white">they might quite like each other?</font>

31:41.120 --> 31:42.200
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

32:09.240 --> 32:12.160
<font color="white">This might be</font>
<font color="white">the very last night of clear skies.</font>

32:12.160 --> 32:14.720
<font color="white">People will be lighting fires soon,</font>
<font color="white">for winter,</font>

32:14.720 --> 32:17.920
<font color="white">and every inch of heaven</font>
<font color="white">will be engulfed in smog.</font>

32:17.920 --> 32:19.520
<font color="yellow">I can see The Plough.</font>

32:21.360 --> 32:22.600
<font color="white">Oh, yes.</font>

32:22.600 --> 32:25.240
<font color="white">The Plough was</font>
<font color="white">my very first constellation.</font>

32:25.240 --> 32:27.800
<font color="yellow">I think mine was The Plaiedes.</font>

32:27.800 --> 32:28.920
<font color="white">The Seven Sisters?</font>

32:30.680 --> 32:33.040
<font color="yellow">I liked the idea</font>
<font color="yellow">of a cluster of girls,</font>

32:33.040 --> 32:35.880
<font color="yellow">all clinging together,</font>
<font color="yellow">in the middle of the heavens.</font>

32:37.120 --> 32:40.360
<font color="white">Can you see</font>
<font color="white">the handle of The Plough? </font><font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

32:40.360 --> 32:43.120
<font color="white">Keep looking</font>
<font color="white">and tell me what you see.</font>

32:46.000 --> 32:49.320
<font color="yellow">It's not one star, it's two,</font>
<font color="yellow">almost overlapping!</font>

32:49.320 --> 32:51.320
<font color="white">Alcor and Mizar.</font>

32:51.320 --> 32:52.440
<font color="white">Congratulations,</font>

32:52.440 --> 32:55.640
<font color="white">you've just passed the eyesight</font>
<font color="white">test for the Roman army.</font>

32:57.080 --> 32:59.760
<font color="white">I thought about that when I went</font>
<font color="white">to do my National Service.</font>

32:59.760 --> 33:03.200
<font color="white">It certainly beat reading</font>
<font color="white">the alphabet backwards off a card,</font>

33:03.200 --> 33:05.760
<font color="white">but there was also</font>
<font color="white">something grimly consoling,</font>

33:05.760 --> 33:07.440
<font color="white">knowing that 2,000 years ago</font>

33:07.440 --> 33:09.480
<font color="white">some other</font>
<font color="white">poor conscripts stood there,</font>

33:09.480 --> 33:11.360
<font color="white">vaguely hoping they might fail.</font>

33:14.040 --> 33:16.200
<font color="white">Will you wake the nuns,</font>
<font color="white">when you let yourself in?</font>

33:16.200 --> 33:19.000
<font color="white">I don't want you on bread</font>
<font color="white">and water for a fortnight.</font>

33:19.000 --> 33:21.360
<font color="yellow">It's almost dawn,</font>
<font color="yellow">they'll be up already.</font>

33:21.360 --> 33:24.960
<font color="yellow">We keep strange hours</font>
<font color="yellow">at Nonnatus House.</font>

33:24.960 --> 33:27.440
<font color="white">How long have the sisters been here?</font>

33:27.440 --> 33:29.640
<font color="yellow">Since 1899, I think.</font>

33:29.640 --> 33:31.640
<font color="white">D'you know where they'll go next?</font>

33:31.640 --> 33:33.960
<font color="yellow">It's all they can do</font>
<font color="yellow">to serve the people here.</font>

33:33.960 --> 33:36.080
<font color="yellow">I don't think</font>
<font color="yellow">they're planning to expand.</font>

33:36.080 --> 33:38.120
<font color="white">I meant after the demolition.</font>

33:38.120 --> 33:39.520
<font color="yellow">Demolition?</font>

33:39.520 --> 33:41.600
<font color="white">It's under</font>
<font color="white">a compulsory purchase order.</font>

33:41.600 --> 33:44.960
<font color="white">This land's been earmarked</font>
<font color="white">for a new through-road.</font>

33:44.960 --> 33:52.200
<font color="white"># Blessed child from above</font>

33:52.200 --> 33:58.680
<font color="white"># His comfort, life and fire of love</font>

33:58.680 --> 34:02.120
<font color="white"># They gave our faith</font>

34:02.120 --> 34:05.920
<font color="white"># Perpetual light</font>

34:07.080 --> 34:14.159
<font color="white"># The darkness of our guided sight</font>

34:14.159 --> 34:22.120
<font color="white"># Father, Son and Holy Spirit</font>

34:24.320 --> 34:30.360
<font color="white"># Amen. #</font>

34:33.520 --> 34:36.480
<font color="cyan">I can't believe it! I just can't!</font>

34:37.800 --> 34:40.440
<font color="lime">I think it's perfectly ridiculous</font>
<font color="lime">banging on about faith</font>

34:40.440 --> 34:42.760
<font color="lime">when the wrecker's ball's</font>
<font color="lime">hanging over our heads!</font>

34:42.760 --> 34:44.320
<font color="yellow">It's not just Nonnatus House.</font>

34:44.320 --> 34:46.520
<font color="yellow">There's a question mark</font>
<font color="yellow">over the parish hall, too!</font>

34:46.520 --> 34:49.199
<font color="white">We're here to serve the mothers</font>
<font color="white">and babies of the district.</font>

34:49.199 --> 34:52.400
<font color="white">What are we supposed to do?</font>
<font color="white">Put up a Big Top in Victoria Park?</font>

34:52.400 --> 34:55.320
<font color="cyan">Yes, and you can buy yourself</font>
<font color="cyan">a caravan, while you're about it,</font>

34:55.320 --> 34:58.480
<font color="cyan">cos you, Peter and the babe</font>
<font color="cyan">are going to need somewhere to live!</font>

34:58.480 --> 35:01.760
<font color="white">We'll be like Flanagan and Allen -</font>
<font color="white">Underneath The Arches!</font>

35:01.760 --> 35:04.720
<font color="white">That's about as much of a joke</font>
<font color="white">as I can manage today,</font>

35:04.720 --> 35:06.400
<font color="white">so please don't start singing.</font>

35:10.320 --> 35:13.520
<font color="lime">Oh, dear.</font>
<font color="lime">Do you suppose it's her hormones?</font>

35:13.520 --> 35:17.640
<font color="cyan">I feel like bursting into tears</font>
<font color="cyan">and I'm not 38 weeks pregnant.</font>

35:17.640 --> 35:20.560
<font color="lime">Right...</font>

35:20.560 --> 35:23.120
<font color="lime">Petri dishes, test tubes, pipettes.</font>

35:23.120 --> 35:25.920
<font color="lime">I want you to count them,</font>
<font color="lime">list them, and wash them.</font>

35:25.920 --> 35:27.640
<font color="white">I hate half-term.</font>

35:27.640 --> 35:30.680
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS</font>

35:30.680 --> 35:31.880
<font color="lime">Morning.</font>

35:31.880 --> 35:33.280
<font color="cyan">'I've been discharged.'</font>

35:34.760 --> 35:35.960
<font color="lime">Sister Bernadette?</font>

35:35.960 --> 35:39.640
<font color="cyan">'I'm supposed</font>
<font color="cyan">to go to Chichester, but I won't.'</font>

35:39.640 --> 35:41.360
<font color="lime">Why's that?</font>

35:43.400 --> 35:44.840
<font color="cyan">I thought...</font>

35:45.960 --> 35:49.480
<font color="cyan">..for a long time,</font>
<font color="cyan">that I was in the wrong place.</font>

35:49.480 --> 35:53.040
<font color="cyan">I wasn't.</font>
<font color="cyan">I was just living the wrong life.</font>

35:55.120 --> 35:56.680
<font color="lime">I wrote to you.</font>

35:56.680 --> 35:58.000
<font color="cyan">Yes.</font>

35:59.320 --> 36:01.720
<font color="lime">I don't know if I said too much.</font>

36:02.960 --> 36:04.440
<font color="lime">Or, or not enough.</font>

36:04.440 --> 36:07.840
<font color="cyan">You said...what was necessary.</font>

36:07.840 --> 36:11.200
<font color="cyan">And I'm coming back to Poplar.</font>

36:11.200 --> 36:12.200
<font color="lime">When?</font>

36:12.200 --> 36:13.360
<font color="cyan">Today.</font>

36:13.360 --> 36:15.800
<font color="cyan">There are procedures</font>
<font color="cyan">to be gone through.</font>

36:15.800 --> 36:18.720
<font color="lime">But it'll be months</font>
<font color="lime">before you're fully fit!</font>

36:18.720 --> 36:22.160
<font color="lime">'You need to rest</font>
<font color="lime">and to convalesce.'</font>

36:22.160 --> 36:25.320
<font color="cyan">I've had enough rest to kill a mule!</font>

36:25.320 --> 36:28.080
<font color="cyan">And I know my own mind,</font>
<font color="cyan">for the first time in many months,</font>

36:28.080 --> 36:30.680
<font color="cyan">which I find</font>
<font color="cyan">remarkably invigorating.</font>

36:30.680 --> 36:32.480
<font color="cyan">I'm on my way to catch the bus.</font>

36:32.480 --> 36:34.680
<font color="lime">You are not travelling 30 miles</font>

36:34.680 --> 36:36.800
<font color="lime">'by public transport!</font>
<font color="lime">Sister Bernadette...'</font>

36:36.800 --> 36:38.240
<font color="cyan">Forgive me.</font>

36:38.240 --> 36:40.360
<font color="cyan">But I don't answer</font>
<font color="cyan">to that name any more.</font>

36:42.160 --> 36:43.600
<font color="lime">Can I help you, Nurse?</font>

36:43.600 --> 36:47.200
<font color="white">I wondered if you wouldn't mind</font>
<font color="white">taking a quick peep at Dolly Smart?</font>

36:47.200 --> 36:48.200
<font color="lime">One moment.</font>

36:50.280 --> 36:51.520
<font color="lime">I'm sorry.</font>

36:51.520 --> 36:54.320
<font color="lime">'I really am. But...duty calls.'</font>

36:54.320 --> 36:55.640
<font color="cyan">I understand.</font>

37:18.680 --> 37:21.840
<font color="lime">Well, it looks as though</font>
<font color="lime">things might be on the move,</font>

37:21.840 --> 37:23.960
<font color="lime">but he's in a good position</font>
<font color="lime">for delivery.</font>

37:23.960 --> 37:27.320
<font color="lime">Nurse Lee is due in shortly.</font>
<font color="lime">I've already drawn up instructions</font>

37:27.320 --> 37:28.800
<font color="lime">for management of labour,</font>

37:28.800 --> 37:31.440
<font color="lime">so I shall leave you in</font>
<font color="lime">the capable hands of Nurse Noakes.</font>

37:31.440 --> 37:33.600
<font color="lime">You're lucky,</font>
<font color="lime">she's one of our finest.</font>

37:42.400 --> 37:44.760
<font color="lime">You're meant</font>
<font color="lime">to be washing equipment.</font>

37:44.760 --> 37:46.840
<font color="cyan">I've finished,</font>
<font color="cyan">and you owe me half a crown.</font>

37:46.840 --> 37:48.600
<font color="cyan">I thought I'd come with you</font>
<font color="cyan">on your rounds.</font>

37:48.600 --> 37:50.120
<font color="lime">I'm not going on my rounds.</font>

38:00.960 --> 38:05.600
<font color="white">Wotcha, Doll! </font><font color="cyan">Dad! Do you know how</font>
<font color="cyan">to send a shore-to-ship telegram?</font>
<font color="white">Why do you want to know?</font>

38:05.600 --> 38:07.600
<font color="cyan">Because I'm in bloody labour,</font>
<font color="cyan">aren't I?</font>

38:07.600 --> 38:10.400
<font color="cyan">You're going to be sending</font>
<font color="cyan">your son-in-law some news!</font>

38:11.400 --> 38:15.840
<font color="white">What about that, then!?</font>

38:28.360 --> 38:30.360
<font color="cyan">If I see her, shall I shout at her?</font>

38:30.360 --> 38:33.440
<font color="cyan">Stop! Sister Bernadette!</font>

38:33.440 --> 38:36.080
<font color="lime">No. Leave the talking to me.</font>

38:46.200 --> 38:49.840
<font color="yellow">Dolly, I think the best thing would</font>
<font color="yellow">be if I break your waters for you.</font>

38:49.840 --> 38:51.640
<font color="yellow">It'll speed things up a little.</font>

38:51.640 --> 38:53.480
<font color="white">Bravo!</font>

39:03.880 --> 39:05.080
<font color="yellow">(Are you all right?)</font>

39:06.080 --> 39:09.960
<font color="white">Never better. Just getting swept</font>
<font color="white">along, in the excitement of it all.</font>

39:09.960 --> 39:14.400
<font color="yellow">I want you to breathe deeply</font>
<font color="yellow">for me, Dolly.</font>

39:14.400 --> 39:19.000
<font color="yellow">That's it.</font>

39:40.800 --> 39:42.800
<font color="yellow">This is it now, Dolly!</font>

39:42.800 --> 39:46.040
<font color="white">SHE MOANS</font>

39:48.840 --> 39:51.400
<font color="white">BABY CRIES</font>

39:51.400 --> 39:54.480
<font color="white">Squealing like a piglet,</font>
<font color="white">just the way we like them!</font>

40:21.760 --> 40:25.240
<font color="cyan">Dad! There's a woman in the wrong</font>
<font color="cyan">clothes and I think it's her.</font>

41:03.640 --> 41:05.440
<font color="lime">What if it had started raining?</font>

41:06.960 --> 41:08.600
<font color="lime">What if you'd got lost?</font>

41:08.600 --> 41:12.160
<font color="cyan">I WAS lost. I got the wrong bus.</font>

41:18.800 --> 41:20.600
<font color="lime">I was on the right road.</font>

41:20.600 --> 41:22.320
<font color="cyan">Yes.</font>

41:25.560 --> 41:28.520
<font color="cyan">I know you so little,</font>
<font color="cyan">but I couldn't be more certain.</font>

41:30.000 --> 41:31.720
<font color="lime">I am completely certain.</font>

41:33.760 --> 41:35.560
<font color="lime">I don't even know your name.</font>

41:35.560 --> 41:37.480
<font color="cyan">Shelagh.</font>

41:37.480 --> 41:38.600
<font color="lime">Patrick.</font>

41:40.120 --> 41:41.160
<font color="cyan">There.</font>

41:42.960 --> 41:44.360
<font color="cyan">We've made a start.</font>

41:55.440 --> 41:56.680
<font color="white">Attention, old chap.</font>

42:00.280 --> 42:04.480
<font color="white">Another grandchild, to add to</font>
<font color="white">your small, but growing, collection.</font>

42:15.200 --> 42:17.320
<font color="lime">Right little bruiser, this one.</font>

42:18.440 --> 42:21.880
<font color="lime">Chip off the old block,</font>
<font color="lime">a proper little boxer's face.</font>

42:23.200 --> 42:25.520
<font color="white">Actually, it's a little girl.</font>

42:26.800 --> 42:30.160
<font color="white">A bit of swelling</font>
<font color="white">around the eyes is quite normal.</font>

42:30.160 --> 42:32.440
<font color="lime">Dolly say</font>
<font color="lime">what she is going to call her?</font>

42:32.440 --> 42:35.600
<font color="white">No. I daresay Freda's a possibility.</font>

42:37.400 --> 42:39.400
<font color="lime">You know something?</font>

42:39.400 --> 42:41.160
<font color="lime">She can call her what she likes.</font>

42:41.160 --> 42:44.080
<font color="lime">It's all just labels,</font>
<font color="lime">really, innit, eh?</font>

42:44.080 --> 42:45.400
<font color="lime">Like on tins of fruit.</font>

42:50.520 --> 42:54.000
<font color="lime">I grew up in my bare feet.</font>

42:54.000 --> 42:57.160
<font color="lime">My dad spent more on beer</font>
<font color="lime">than he did on shoe leather.</font>

42:57.160 --> 43:00.640
<font color="lime">I used to think, when I have kids,</font>
<font color="lime">I'm going give them shoes,</font>

43:00.640 --> 43:03.400
<font color="lime">hot dinners, 'appy home...</font>

43:04.760 --> 43:06.320
<font color="lime">..and I managed all three...</font>

43:07.720 --> 43:09.360
<font color="lime">..until Hitler intervened.</font>

43:10.360 --> 43:13.080
<font color="lime">When the bomb dropped,</font>
<font color="lime">I weren't there.</font>

43:15.200 --> 43:17.960
<font color="lime">And that's what makes you</font>
<font color="lime">a parent, Nurse Noakes.</font>

43:19.960 --> 43:21.120
<font color="lime">Proximity.</font>

43:23.840 --> 43:25.720
<font color="lime">They don't sell that in the shops.</font>

43:25.720 --> 43:27.280
<font color="white">No.</font>

43:30.160 --> 43:31.320
<font color="lime">You all right, Nurse?</font>

43:35.280 --> 43:40.240
<font color="yellow">Chummy. Something tells me</font>
<font color="yellow">your working day is over.</font>

43:40.240 --> 43:42.640
<font color="white">Something tells me yours isn't.</font>

43:45.880 --> 43:48.640
<font color="cyan">One delivery pack</font>
<font color="cyan">on its way to the first floor!</font>

43:48.640 --> 43:51.400
<font color="lime">Water's hotting up</font>
<font color="lime">and I'm bringing more towels.</font>

43:52.760 --> 43:55.680
<font color="cyan">We can't give Chummy an enema!</font>
<font color="cyan">She's our friend.</font>

43:55.680 --> 43:58.000
<font color="lime">If you don't do it, I will.</font>

44:01.920 --> 44:04.320
<font color="yellow">Come on Chummy! On the bed.</font>

44:04.320 --> 44:06.560
<font color="yellow">"High, hot and a hell of a lot!"</font>

44:06.560 --> 44:08.520
<font color="white">No. No. You absolute beasts!</font>

44:08.520 --> 44:11.560
<font color="cyan">Chummy, you'll have to surrender</font>
<font color="cyan">or Sister Evangelina will come</font>

44:11.560 --> 44:12.560
<font color="cyan">and do it.</font>

44:12.560 --> 44:15.560
<font color="cyan">And I wouldn't put it past her</font>
<font color="cyan">to chuck in extra soap!</font>

44:15.560 --> 44:17.480
<font color="white">Can't we just pretend?</font>

44:17.480 --> 44:21.240
<font color="white">Send out a chamber pot with a cloth</font>
<font color="white">draped over it, like a sort of ruse?</font>

44:26.720 --> 44:31.160
<font color="yellow">Breathe it away Chummy,</font>
<font color="yellow">breathe it away.</font>

44:35.640 --> 44:37.280
<font color="white">Everything that you handed over</font>

44:37.280 --> 44:40.800
<font color="white">when you entered the Order</font>
<font color="white">was held in trust for your lifetime,</font>

44:40.800 --> 44:43.760
<font color="white">or until such time</font>
<font color="white">as you renounced your vows.</font>

44:43.760 --> 44:46.920
<font color="cyan">I don't want anything back.</font>
<font color="cyan">I've been given so much...</font>

44:46.920 --> 44:49.080
<font color="white">This is the procedure</font>
<font color="white">we must follow.</font>

44:49.080 --> 44:53.560
<font color="white">There is something in the region</font>
<font color="white">of £100 to be returned to you,</font>

44:53.560 --> 44:56.120
<font color="white">once you have signed</font>
<font color="white">the final papers.</font>

45:22.920 --> 45:24.560
<font color="white">If you would like some quiet time,</font>

45:24.560 --> 45:26.960
<font color="white">you're welcome to use the chapel</font>
<font color="white">before you leave.</font>

45:26.960 --> 45:28.200
<font color="cyan">Thank you, Sister.</font>

45:29.640 --> 45:31.840
<font color="cyan">But I have so many things to do.</font>

45:31.840 --> 45:33.080
<font color="white">Very well.</font>

45:47.720 --> 45:51.320
<font color="white">May God bless you,</font>
<font color="white">my dear, good friend.</font>

45:53.480 --> 45:54.840
<font color="cyan">And may He bless you, too.</font>

46:20.440 --> 46:21.800
<font color="white">Is there any news?</font>

46:21.800 --> 46:23.760
<font color="lime">It's a baby,</font>
<font color="lime">not a lubricated penguin,</font>

46:23.760 --> 46:25.680
<font color="lime">they don't come sliding out,</font>
<font color="lime">to order.</font>

46:25.680 --> 46:28.400
<font color="lime">And you needn't think we'll be</font>
<font color="lime">running in with meals on trays.</font>

46:28.400 --> 46:31.320
<font color="lime">You get peckish,</font>
<font color="lime">you ask directions to the bread bin.</font>

46:44.800 --> 46:48.520
<font color="cyan">That's it. That's it...</font>

46:49.560 --> 46:51.920
<font color="white">The bally things just go on and on.</font>

46:51.920 --> 46:54.800
<font color="yellow">You're doing brilliantly, Chummy.</font>

46:54.800 --> 46:56.560
<font color="yellow">We'll examine you</font>
<font color="yellow">in a minute or two,</font>

46:56.560 --> 46:58.120
<font color="yellow">and see how things are progressing.</font>

46:58.120 --> 47:00.640
<font color="white">I wouldn't thumb my nose</font>
<font color="white">at a spot of pethidine.</font>

47:00.640 --> 47:02.840
<font color="cyan">Of course. We'll get it organised.</font>

47:04.920 --> 47:08.000
<font color="white">Waters... I felt my waters.</font>

47:14.520 --> 47:16.880
<font color="white">WHISPERS: </font><font color="cyan">Get Sister Julienne.</font>

47:26.600 --> 47:28.160
<font color="yellow">I need an ambulance, please.</font>

47:28.160 --> 47:30.680
<font color="white">'Can I have the address, please?'</font>

47:30.680 --> 47:33.200
<font color="yellow">Nonnatus House,</font>
<font color="yellow">Leyland Street, Poplar.</font>

47:33.200 --> 47:35.000
<font color="white">'Can you give me anymore details?'</font>

47:35.000 --> 47:37.720
<font color="yellow">It's a suspected</font>
<font color="yellow">placental abruption.</font>

47:37.720 --> 47:39.360
<font color="yellow">The mother has haemorrhaged.</font>

47:39.360 --> 47:40.720
<font color="white">'Has the baby been born?'</font>

47:40.720 --> 47:43.280
<font color="yellow">No. She's still in labour.</font>

47:43.280 --> 47:46.000
<font color="white">'And baby's heartbeat?'</font>

47:46.000 --> 47:48.680
<font color="yellow">As far as we know,</font>
<font color="yellow">the baby's still alive.</font>

47:48.680 --> 47:50.520
<font color="white">We need her on her left side</font>

47:50.520 --> 47:52.840
<font color="white">to increase the blood</font>
<font color="white">supply to the baby.</font>

47:52.840 --> 47:55.400
<font color="cyan">Come on Chummy, that's it.</font>
<font color="cyan">That's it.</font>

47:55.400 --> 47:56.560
<font color="lime">Oxygen.</font>

47:56.560 --> 47:59.280
<font color="white">SHE SCREAMS</font>
<font color="cyan">It's all right. It's all right.</font>

47:59.280 --> 48:01.040
<font color="lime">And she needs pethidine!</font>

48:02.640 --> 48:04.240
<font color="lime">Here.</font>

48:04.240 --> 48:07.760
<font color="white">Breath deeply.</font>
<font color="white">This will help you and the baby.</font>

48:17.080 --> 48:20.640
<font color="yellow">Try to keep calm. Chummy, stay calm.</font>

48:28.160 --> 48:31.240
<font color="white"># Catch a falling star... #</font>

48:33.360 --> 48:34.840
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

48:36.200 --> 48:37.800
<font color="yellow">Catch a falling star?</font>

48:39.400 --> 48:41.160
<font color="white">Never let it...</font>

48:41.160 --> 48:43.480
<font color="white">fade away...</font>

49:04.720 --> 49:07.560
<font color="cyan">Just one of you, please.</font>

49:07.560 --> 49:08.960
<font color="lime">Go on.</font>

49:08.960 --> 49:11.160
<font color="lime">And you make sure you hold her hand!</font>

49:53.560 --> 49:57.280
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS</font>

50:00.680 --> 50:02.120
<font color="cyan">'Nonnatus House...'</font>

50:02.120 --> 50:05.000
<font color="lime">I've watched people</font>
<font color="lime">do this time after time.</font>

50:05.000 --> 50:08.400
<font color="lime">Sitting waiting for news,</font>

50:08.400 --> 50:10.480
<font color="lime">not knowing, hoping.</font>

50:10.480 --> 50:14.600
<font color="lime">Never really known what they felt...</font>

50:14.600 --> 50:15.800
<font color="lime">until now.</font>

50:20.800 --> 50:23.240
<font color="yellow">She's still in theatre.</font>

50:23.240 --> 50:25.040
<font color="yellow">There was another haemorrhage.</font>

50:32.440 --> 50:35.160
<font color="cyan">We haven't got</font>
<font color="cyan">a telephone number for Madeira.</font>

50:35.160 --> 50:37.800
<font color="cyan">Her family don't even know</font>
<font color="cyan">what's happened.</font>

50:40.760 --> 50:42.440
<font color="yellow">Yes, they do.</font>

50:42.440 --> 50:44.960
<font color="yellow">Chummy's family's here in this room.</font>

51:12.280 --> 51:15.280
<font color="white">MATURE JENNY: </font><font color="yellow">'Throughout</font>
<font color="yellow">that endless day and night,</font>

51:15.280 --> 51:18.560
<font color="yellow">'as we waited for news</font>
<font color="yellow">that didn't come,</font>

51:18.560 --> 51:22.640
<font color="yellow">'it seemed we had never been closer,</font>

51:22.640 --> 51:27.320
<font color="yellow">'never more subsumed</font>
<font color="yellow">into a single task.</font>

51:48.200 --> 51:52.520
<font color="yellow">'Many find the concept</font>
<font color="yellow">of holy silence puzzling.</font>

51:55.160 --> 51:58.560
<font color="yellow">'But as we worked and prayed,</font>

51:58.560 --> 52:01.040
<font color="yellow">there was no need to speak, at all.'</font>

52:46.000 --> 52:47.040
<font color="white">How is she?</font>

54:13.920 --> 54:15.040
<font color="lime">Camilla.</font>

54:18.080 --> 54:19.520
<font color="lime">We've got a little boy.</font>

54:35.400 --> 54:37.600
<font color="white">A boy?</font>

54:40.680 --> 54:42.480
<font color="white">Hello, little bean.</font>

54:45.560 --> 54:47.720
<font color="white">It's all right, I'm here.</font>

55:16.640 --> 55:19.080
<font color="cyan">Hello, Patrick.</font>

55:19.080 --> 55:20.480
<font color="lime">Hello, Shelagh.</font>

55:22.920 --> 55:23.960
<font color="lime">This is for you.</font>

55:25.400 --> 55:27.920
<font color="lime">From me. And somebody else.</font>

55:40.640 --> 55:42.400
<font color="cyan">"Please will you marry my dad?"</font>

56:25.000 --> 56:27.760
<font color="white">MATURE JENNY:</font>
<font color="yellow">'Through the telescope of memory,</font>

56:27.760 --> 56:32.120
<font color="yellow">'I see now the convent</font>
<font color="yellow">was our pole star,</font>

56:32.120 --> 56:35.280
<font color="yellow">'a guiding light</font>
<font color="yellow">for those who worked there</font>

56:35.280 --> 56:37.960
<font color="yellow">'and the people that we served.'</font>

56:39.600 --> 56:44.560
<font color="white"># You turned to me</font>
<font color="white">With a kiss in your eyes... #</font>

56:44.560 --> 56:48.080
<font color="yellow">'Dolly's little girl</font>
<font color="yellow">was christened Samantha,</font>

56:48.080 --> 56:52.880
<font color="yellow">'a rather modern name, to which some</font>
<font color="yellow">people never became accustomed.'</font>

56:52.880 --> 56:56.200
<font color="white"># When your lips cling to mine</font>

56:56.200 --> 57:00.080
<font color="white"># It's wonderful, wonderful</font>

57:00.080 --> 57:02.480
<font color="white"># Oh, so wonderful... #</font>

57:02.480 --> 57:05.160
